In re BEAUPRE, Jack Raymond(MR 20233)

Bourbonnais, IL

Order of the Court:

... The petition by the Administrator of the Attorney Registration and Disciplinary Commission for leave to file exceptions to the report and recommendation of the Review Board is allowed. Respondent Jack Raymond Beaupre is suspended from the practice of law for 90 days.

Suspension effective October 17, 2005.

Respondent Jack Raymond Beaupre shall reimburse the Disciplinary Fund for any Client Protection payments arising from his conduct prior to the termination of the period of suspension.
